Sometimes I feel bad for Maan sahab, we haven't given him what he truely deserves. Such an eminent personality , voice as divine as it could be, touches heart from grassroot to the top, a great human being. We haven't given him what he deserves....
He deserves to be Bharat Ratna for preserving soul of Punjabi language and Punjabiaat which has been compromised by singers who just sing for fame and money... Proud of people like Daljit who are preserving legacy... We salute Maan Sahab and his work.. May god bless him
